Messages API Reference Documentation

This is our stand alone messaging API.

Paths

URL: https://dcfa18db-f8d9-4e48-8fad-3f4dfcc7386e.mock.pstmn.io/v1/messages

POST Add a message

Request Body:
  • #/components/schemas/Message
Responses:
  • 201 - Successful add of message.
    • Content
      • application/json - Message
  • 500 - Unexpected error
    • Content
      • application/json - Error

GET Retrieve messages

Parameters
  • q (true) - Query to filter the messages
  • limit (true) - Limit the records returned.
  • page (true) - Which page is being returned.
Responses:
  • 200 - Successful add of message.
    • Content
      • application/json - Messages
  • 500 - Unexpected error
    • Content
      • application/json - Error

URL: https://dcfa18db-f8d9-4e48-8fad-3f4dfcc7386e.mock.pstmn.io/v1/messages/{messageId}

PARAMETERS

GET Read a message

Responses:
  • 200 - Successful return of single message.
    • Content
      • application/json - Message
  • 500 - Unexpected error
    • Content
      • application/json - Error

PUT Read a message

Request Body:
  • #/components/schemas/Message
Responses:
  • 204 - The message corresponding to the provided `messageId`
  • 500 - Unexpected error
    • Content
      • application/json - Error

DELETE Deletes a message

Responses:
  • 200 - Successful deletion of message.
    • Content
      • application/json - Message
  • 500 - Unexpected error
    • Content
      • application/json - Error

Schema

MessageId

Type: string

Messages

Type: array

Items:

  • Message

Message

Type: object

Properties:

  • id ()
  • to (string)
  • from (string)
  • subject (string)
  • body (string)

Required:

  • id
  • name
  • type

Error

Type: object

Properties:

  • message (string)

Required:

  • message
